text: The blacktail moray eel (Gymnothorax kolpos) is a moray eel found in the western Atlantic Ocean.Gymnothorax kolpos at www.fishbase.org. It was first named by Böhlke and Böhlke in 1980.Common names for Gymnothorax kolpos at www.fishbase.org. ==References== blacktail moray Category:Fauna of the Southeastern United States Category:Fish of the Gulf of Mexico blacktail moray
